**Project Title: EssenceLang - Unveiling the Core Principles of Programming Languages in Racket**

# EssenceLang

Welcome to EssenceLang, an ambitious project that embarks on the implementation journey of parsers and interpreters for four distinct custom languages. Each language, inspired by the principles outlined in the recommended book "Essentials Of Programming Languages," is crafted to illustrate essential concepts such as lexical scoping, recursion, and foundational language constructs.

